{"tid":638938,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"香港海關掃蕩全港手機黑店　破獲逾百假手機拘19 人","createTime":"2018-04-23T06:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T00:45:22.000Z","uid":9960,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"54285c717d32ca4e95751d7581b990bfeaccb0ef","tid":638938,"uid":9960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:34:11.000Z","msg":"在非蘋果授權渠道購買 iPhone 或配件，你可能需要額外留神，因為一些手機店可能銷售冒牌手機或配件。<br />\n<br />\n香港海關因應公眾舉報，在上周末採取代號「雪豹」的全港執法行動，搜查全港 14 個地點包括 12 家店鋪，<span style=\"color: red;\">發現 100 部懷疑假冒或應用虛假商品說明的智能手機</span>包括 iPhone 8、Galaxy S8 以及小米手機，以及 3400 件懷疑假冒配件，總值 150 萬港圓，行動中拘捕 17 個店主和店員，另外也破獲了 1 個分別在深水埗和青衣設倉的分銷集團，搜出 64 部假冒手機和 3000 件假冒的配件，並拘捕一名 32 歲男性主腦和一名 34 歲女性成員。<br />\n<br />\n海關大舉掃蕩假冒手機是因為有民眾舉報一些手機<span style=\"color: red;\">黑店將二手機舊機或水貨重新包裝當新機以原價一半左右出售</span>，香港蘋果日報報導指，有用家從手機黑店買了所謂的「新機」回家後不能開機，回手機店要求退款不果，最後向海關舉報。<br />\n<br />\n海關在行動中表示在 5 月 1 日「黃金周」期間海關會加強執法，不排除有更多人被捕，並呼籲消費者購買產品時光顧信譽良好的商戶，購買前應仔細檢查所購買的貨品。海關更新增一個舉報罪案的專用電郵帳戶方便民眾舉報。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">先達多家手機店拉閘</span><br />\n<br />\n在「雪豹」行動期間，海關關員闖入香港主要手機市場先達廣場，在不同樓層搜查多家手機店，看看手機店有沒有聘用黑工或售賣冒牌手機零件和配件，受事件影響多家手機店拉閘關門不營業。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180422/large/1524381836_dd69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180422%2Flarge%2F1524381836_dd69.jpg&h=f62e6c8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行動中共檢獲100部懷疑冒牌智能電話。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180422/large/1524381838_1fd3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180422%2Flarge%2F1524381838_1fd3.jpg&h=ccb0b459&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行動中共檢獲約3000件懷疑冒牌智能電話配件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/hk-customs-seize-smartphone-shop-which-sold-fake-iphone_03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2Fhk-customs-seize-smartphone-shop-which-sold-fake-iphone_03.jpg&h=5a7a29af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180422/large/1524381840_cf4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180422%2Flarge%2F1524381840_cf4f.jpg&h=bc3815c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先達廣場內，仍有部分店舖繼續營業。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">先達狗</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6b1688fb039b6baf3a39b3412474c8fb134920","tid":638938,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T09:50:01.000Z","msg":"係咪賣 華強北  組裝機, 當新機賣. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,"},{"pid":"3a46501fdac7d39e768e739127b9399140951dc7","tid":638938,"uid":51623,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T09:55:17.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打整個打拉閘list岀嚟？"},{"pid":"768a87ee5bfcc22fa2b2f95da1333968ef5c7184","tid":638938,"uid":71342,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3a46501fdac7d39e768e739127b9399140951dc7","tid":638938,"uid":51623,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T09:55:17.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打整個打拉閘list岀嚟？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T10:01:20.000Z","msg":"當佢全場都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99da89b58e10d33443a4bbfbd9a0a9fb535e610b","tid":638938,"uid":1085,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T11:07:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74fc0cc5c43c58b39cca31ff3b285886b0567468","tid":638938,"uid":39305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T11:28:39.000Z","msg":"經驗係 地下個層賣假野多D，因為佢收逢有Iphone出個陣地下個層收機價係低過一樓好多，佢地靠賣機賺錢"},{"pid":"989cbfd5ef02cde902b18693dd915d